# Yala Safari Website - Cursor Rules

## Project Overview
Safari tour booking website for Yala National Park in Sri Lanka featuring wildlife tours, booking forms, and testimonials.

## Design System

### Color Palette
- **Primary Background**: Light gray (#e6e6e6) to white gradient
- **Primary Color**: Dark green (#034123)
- **Accent Color**: Orange (#f26b21)
- **Highlight Color**: Yellow (#fee000)
- **Text Primary**: Dark green (#034123)
- **Text Secondary**: Dark gray (#333333)
- **Card Background**: White with subtle borders

### Typography
- **Headings**: Sans-serif, bold, large scale
- **Body Text**: Sans-serif, medium weight
- **Font Sizes**: 
  - Hero heading: 72px+
  - Section headings: 32-36px
  - Body text: 16-18px
  - Small text: 14px

### Spacing
- Section padding: 80-120px vertical
- Card padding: 40-60px
- Button padding: 16px 32px
- Grid gaps: 24-32px

## Component Guidelines

### Navigation Bar
```
- Sticky header that starts translucent/white and gains a solid white background + subtle shadow once the user scrolls (~12px)
- Logo/wordmark on left (icon + brand text) in dark green (#034123)
- Primary navigation links: Home, Packages, About, Blog, Rooms & Taxi, Contact (dark green #034123 text)
- Prominent "Book Now" CTA (desktop: right-aligned button in orange #f26b21, mobile: included in menu list)
- Mobile: accessible hamburger button (`aria-controls`, `aria-expanded`) that locks body scroll while open
- Provide smooth 0.2s–0.3s transitions for color/background changes to keep motion professional
```

### Home / Landing Page
```
- Full-page light gradient backdrop (#e6e6e6 to white) with clean card layers
- Hero: immersive photography with light overlay (20–30% opacity), headline in 4–6xl range, accent badge + paired CTAs (`primary` uses #f26b21, `secondary` uses bordered #034123)
- Featured cards: clean white background with subtle shadows (border-gray/20, bg-white, soft shadows) and hover lift (translate-y)
- About: accent highlights (#fee000) behind imagery, rounded-3xl photography with conservation-led captions
- Reviews: dual platform cards with gradient headers, testimonials in 3-column grid using yellow star icons (#fee000) and platform badges
- Final CTA: gradient band (#034123 to #f26b21), uppercase microcopy, paired buttons (primary #f26b21, secondary outline #034123) aligned for desktop + stacked on mobile
```

### Hero Section
```
- Full viewport height background image (wildlife/safari theme)
- Light overlay (20–30% white) for text readability
- Centered content with:
  - Large heading (brand name) in dark green (#034123)
  - Subtitle/tagline in dark gray
  - Primary CTA button (orange #f26b21)
- Background image: High-quality wildlife photography
```

