## Buttons
```css
Primary Button:
- Background: #f26b21 (orange)
- Color: white
- Padding: 16px 32px
- Border radius: 8px
- Hover: Darken 10% or use #034123 (dark green)
- No border

Secondary Button:
- Background: transparent
- Border: 2px solid #034123 (dark green)
- Color: #034123 (dark green)
- Same padding and radius as primary
- Hover: Background #034123, color white

Accent/Highlight Button:
- Background: #fee000 (yellow)
- Color: #034123 (dark green)
- Same padding and radius as primary
- Hover: Brighten or darken text
```

## Forms
```css
Input Fields:
- Background: #e6e6e6 (light gray) or white
- Border: 1px solid rgba(3, 65, 35, 0.2) (dark green with opacity)
- Border radius: 6px
- Padding: 12px 16px
- Color: #034123 (dark green)
- Placeholder: rgba(3, 65, 35, 0.5) (dark green with opacity)

Focus State:
- Border color: #f26b21 (orange)
- Outline: none
- Background: white (if using gray background)
```

## Responsive Breakpoints
```
- Mobile: 0-768px
- Tablet: 769px-1024px
- Desktop: 1025px+

Mobile Changes:
- Stack navigation vertically
- Single column layouts
- Reduced font sizes (20-30%)
- Reduced padding (50%)
```

## Image Guidelines
```
- Wildlife photos: High resolution, dramatic lighting
- Safari vehicles: Show authentic safari jeeps
- Background images: Light overlays (20–30% white) for text readability on light theme
- Profile images: Circular crop, 60-80px diameter
- Optimize for web (WebP format preferred)
```

## Animation Guidelines
```
- Subtle transitions: 0.3s ease
- Hover effects: Scale(1.05) or brightness adjustments
- Scroll animations: Fade in on view (optional)
- Button interactions: Quick feedback (0.2s)
- No excessive animations - keep it professional
```

## Content Tone
```
- Professional yet adventurous
- Emphasis on natural beauty and wildlife
- Safety and expertise highlighted
- Sri Lankan cultural context
- Environmental consciousness
```

## Technical Stack Recommendations
```
- HTML5 semantic markup
- CSS3 with flexbox/grid
- Vanilla JavaScript or React
- Date picker library for form
- Lazy loading for images
- Mobile-first approach
```

## Accessibility
```
- Alt text for all images
- ARIA labels for navigation
- Keyboard navigation support
- Sufficient color contrast (WCAG AA)
- Focus indicators visible
- Form labels properly associated
```

## SEO Considerations
```
- Semantic HTML structure
- Meta descriptions with keywords
- Image alt text with context
- H1-H6 hierarchy maintained
- Schema markup for tours/reviews
- Fast loading times
```